{"tid":1852722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文：年假後可日產420萬個口罩, 政府統一採購","createTime":"2020-01-30T14:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:49:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfcb35ad5aa19460b8d09cd21fb1f867016dd79","tid":1852722,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505677-20200130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505677-20200130.htm&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=32449a6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505677-20200130.htm&h=bd685c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505677-20200130.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 蔡英文：年假後可日產420萬個口罩 政府統一採購<br />\n2020-01-30 HKT 16:23<br />\n<br />\n在台灣，蔡英文總統說會加強管控防疫物資，應對武漢的新型肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n至於台灣民眾關心的口罩問題，蔡英文說年假後會逐步恢復生產，每天可生產420萬個，政府相關部門會統一採購、調控、定價，並追蹤口罩產量與存貨，確保島內供求情況，並會嚴格偵查囤積及抬價等問題。<br />\n<br />\n針對疫情對經濟構成的衝擊，蔡英文說已指示相關部門應對，包括穩定股市及匯市、減少短期心理因素衝擊、輔導企業做好防疫、對受衝擊的產業提供紓困措施等。她又慰問在防疫前線的各部門人員。"},{"pid":"7c155153ebc5aefcc21e87c6b7fcdc37bd99e8ff","tid":1852722,"uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"蔡英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41bf3a59cdcb14714dc4d14348f9fda3299160cb","tid":1852722,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"但都唔夠6分1內需"},{"pid":"d35174158678c1f0ba8c874d07bddd285491f6db","tid":1852722,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"救香港呀，英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c303f809a026